produce switching noise only during lock, the
treshold circuitry (TVDD) on the other hand is
expected to have mostly DC consumption. The
TVDD and XVDD are thus supplied from the
same LDO, yet the XVDD is still isolated by a
ferrite to reduce the chance of noise being
